_sText:
*Screen shots were taken from a much, much older version!  The new one looks a lot better.  i just have no time to take and upload them.  Sorry!

This map is a lot like the old arcade game "Jump Man"  It is pretty fun.

i made the original version as a prototype for another map, and it turned out to be quite fun.  I updated it for the Gamers syndicate or [G`SyN] because they are so great.

fixes:
*Textures... a whole lot of texture fixes
*The Terrorists buttons now take 2 seconds, rather then 1.25 seconds to reset, making barrel spam a lot less of an instance.
*the firepit has been fixed
*and a fun new grenade ending!
